  • Constructor Details

    • Player

      public Player(String userName, String gamerTag, String map, String tribeName, int ap, int seen) throws InvalidNameException, InvalidGamertagException, InvalidTribeNameException
      Creates a new Player based on the information given by the user. This is the constructor that will be called on by the bot when the user is registering in the #register channel in the Bliss discord server.
      Parameters:
      userName - The in-game name of the Player registering.
      gamerTag - The GamerTag of the Player registering.
      map - The Main map that the Player plays on.
      tribeName - The name of the tribe that a player is a member of.
      ap - The amount of AP a player has.
      seen - The number of times the player has been seen in a week.
      Throws:
      InvalidNameException - if the player's name is invalid.
      InvalidGamertagException - if the player's gamertag is invalid.
      InvalidTribeNameException - if the player's tribe name is invalid.
